== Notes ==
* '''Colours''' are borrowed from {{tl|IUCN status}} (CR&nbsp;{{nowrap|#CC3333}}, EN&nbsp;#CC6633, VU&nbsp;#CC9900, EX&nbsp;black, CD&nbsp;#006666); there is no official EPBC colour scheme, and the taxobox path ({{tl|Species conservation status}} via [[Module:Conservation status]]) uses greyscale ladder icons rather than coloured badges. Always show the text code alongside the badge for accessibility.
* The external link targets the SPRAT species profile (the same URL pattern as {{tl|SPRAT}}). SPRAT can lag the legislative [[Federal Register of Legislation|List of Threatened Species]] slightly.
* Invalid codes are placed in [[:Category:EPBC status templates with invalid parameters]].

